    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主状态流转画出来：Pending可以通过Approve到Approved，通过Reject到Rejected，通过Delete到Deleted；Approved和Rejected也都可以Delete到Deleted。起点EtcdCluster创建评论进入Pending，终点Deleted流向RedisCache。",
      "elements_involved": [
